Inspect an air rifle range

The RSO must ensure the range and all equipment are safe to use:

•Check the perimeter of the range and/or   access points to be sure no one can accidentally enter the range;

 

•Check the rifles for safe operation; and

 

•Check target backstops, and the area behind for anything that can be damaged by stray pellets.

Click on each biathlon target to get important information. You must view all of the targets.
